from Felia (Swe Phone company)

Contact him on 2:200/123.8 FidoNet... And ask for ANI things...
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Usage" "Usage"
@{b}Usage:@{ub}

Hmm... Just log on the BBS ! :-)
Or type ANI somewhere in the BBS.
@ENDNODE

